headline: Creditors claim millions as freight bankruptcy filings roll in
summary: Creditors are claiming millions of dollars from two trucking companies and a distribution service provider after all three companies filed for bankruptcy at the start of this week. The post Creditors claim millions as freight bankruptcy filings roll in appeared first on FreightWaves.
